# Task Manager App

A simple console-based task manager written in C++.  
It allows users to:

- Add tasks with names and optional due dates
- Mark tasks as completed
- View pending or completed tasks
- Delete tasks

## Features

- Object-oriented design using C++ classes
- Efficient task storage using STL containers
- Input validation and basic error handling
- Clean terminal UI

## How to Run

1. Make sure you have a C++ compiler installed (e.g., `g++`)
2. Compile the project:
   ```bash
   g++ main.cpp -o task_manager
